originalText.text: 1-888-Type It Up produced a letter perfect, lengthy document with highly technical terms on time and in full compliance with the accelerated deadline agreed upon. Their pricing is fair and reasonable. I will most definitely use them again!

originalText.text: Wow!  I contacted  1888-TYPE-IT-UP at 6:00 am and was contacted within 1 hour about my project.  I needed a 60- page pdf legal pleading full of formatting errors and redlines re-typed into a clean Word document in 3 calendar days over a holiday weekend.  My project was delivered early and perfect.  Before the project started, I was contacted via phone to review questions about the project and my preferences.  The attention to detail to assure a project to my completion was smart, well placed and a pleasure.

originalText.text: I had almost 100 handwritten pages -- memoirs hand-written by a woman over eighty. I wanted a 'true' copy, without any errors corrected, transcribed into a text file readable by computer. The results were perfect. The price was reasonable. The turn around time was a week less than promised. I am happy to recommend them.
